{"tid":1282439,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主派籲限期前表態反對確認書：炸爆選管會電郵 (附template)","createTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T07:14:32.000Z","uid":107178,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f340ffadbc41c22a6223871d594af623706f567c","tid":1282439,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"區議會換屆選舉將於11月24日舉行，選管會早前發表區議會選舉活動建議指引，建議在區選中引入「確認書」制度，要求參選人簽署聲明擁護《基本法》及保證效忠香港特別行政區，諮詢期本月10日屆滿。民主派議員批評政府利用確認書DQ參選人，剝削選舉權利，呼籲市民以提意見促選管會撤銷「確認書」。<br />\n<br />\n早前參加鄉郊選舉也被DQ的民主派議員朱凱廸呼籲市民限期前「炸爆佢（選管會）email」，向政府表達市民反對確認書的意見，形容是「無成本、唔怕做」，要以強大民意力量，壓制政府進行「政治審查」的氣燄。他稱，雖然確認書與DQ無直接關係，即使參選人簽署確認書仍有可能被DQ，但亦不能增加確認書的正當性，市民要盡力表達反對意見。參與九西補選但被DQ的前議員劉小麗指，不能讓政府合理化DQ參選人的行為，必須趕在截止前表達反對確認書的意見，她批評政府早前取消諮詢會的決定匪夷所思，與林鄭口中樂於溝通背道而馳，她又指除了書面意見，亦會與民主派政團組織示威行動，表達對確認書的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n選管會原定於上月25日就區議會選舉活動建議指引進行公眾諮詢，不過在「反送中」運動浪潮下，選管會以安全理由取消公眾諮詢大會，令市民無法當面向選舉主任表達反確認書意見。選管會暫時未有提及會否改期重辦公眾諮詢大會，<span style=\"color: red;\">如就建議指引內容有書面意見，可以從三個方式表達：郵寄（香港灣仔港灣道二十五號海港中心十樓選管會秘書處）、傳真（2511 1682）及電郵（eacenq@eac.hk）。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Template</span><br />\n<br />\nRe: Opinion on the Disqualification of Candidacy<br />\n<br />\nTo whom it may concern,<br />\n<br />\nConcerning your public conference supposedly to be held on 25.6.2019 was cancelled, I am writing to express my objection and anger on your decision to disqualify the candidacy of several people in certain previous elections.<br />\n<br />\nI would like to show my great concern and worries on the disqualification of candidacy because of his or her political belief, and the case of previous legislator Lau Siu-lai has raised my attention. According to that case, her candidacy in the Legislative Council Election was rejected as the returning officer Franco Kwok Wai-fun said he was unconvinced that she had genuinely ditched &ldquo;self-determination&rdquo;&ndash; a position deemed as tantamount to splitting Hong Kong from China.<br />\n<br />\nI believe that the majority of Hong Kong citizens would question the decision mentioned above. As one of the ordinary citizens, I would like to ask that how the officer has come to the so-called conclusion that Lau 'had genuinely ditched &ldquo;self-determination&quot; ' and by what examination(s) the officer had made before such a conclusion. Even worse, I strongly believe that the decision of disqualification of candidacy severely harms the freedom of election, a core value which has been preserved and respected in the city for decades, and it therefore should be definitely reviewed and avoided.<br />\n<br />\nAfter all, I believe that the cancellation of the public conference was an unwise decision as it stopped the public from giving their opinions on the current running election systems, and you, as one of the most important governmental authorities, should make responses to the questions and demands from the general public as soon as possible.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely, <br />\nA Hong Kong citizen<br />\n<br />\n篇新聞講劉小麗就寫左佢，大家send時可以改其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7707efb42446b919d787e14650f22d16297b6fb","tid":1282439,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:44:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"802f0a8ab0248db46ae9de5fac5abee5ba16e140","tid":1282439,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:45:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"74246704844c235a97915735dcc7b220b948923a","tid":1282439,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd367070be120ee9e4536db78381f54a18ceea73","tid":1282439,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T14:45:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c1731804cef86d92f80704dc808691413f7964d1","tid":1282439,"uid":107178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":